metadata.name: THE GOLF BALL TROPHY
metadata.description:
The first trophy made by our team for WORLD FINAL DUBAI in United Arab Emirates , Dubai . which is made in both physical and NFT form, is the 30-person NFT version.  The physical version of this art work is designed and made for 18 winners of the contest , which are presented to the 18 main winners , which are gold first , silver second and transparent third .  The date of tournament  November 27-30, 2022 by WORLD AMATEUR MATCH RACE .

Designed by Sahar Sobati
